Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ffmpeg, python3-pyside6.qtwidgets
Description: Offline subtitle generator and editor for vertical videos
 GLDFrames creates, edits, previews, and burns subtitles into short-form
 vertical videos using local speech recognition and FFmpeg.
